    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207931>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43 – 46. Dentalion quadrifer sp. nov., female. 43. Head frontal. 44. Mesosoma dorsal. 45. Propodeum dorsal. 46. Head dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207931/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207932>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47 – 53. Dentalion spp., females. 47. D. pinguicornis sp. nov., mesosoma lateral. 48. D. pinguicornis, right-hand lateral panel of metanotum, arrow points to longitudinal carina that divides panel into two about equal-sized parts. 49. D. noyesi sp. nov., hind femur lateral. 50. D. apertum sp. nov., first funicular segment. 51. D. apon sp. nov., base of forewing. 52. D. apertum, base of forewing. 53. D. noyesi, base of forewing. Abbreviations: cs = costal cell with row of setae; sp = speculum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

